Build your own open-source stream controller deck for Lumia Stream Premium. (version for free users coming soon)
With 36 programmable keys, support for both short and long presses, an integrated LCD for alerts and messages, and a built-in virtual pet, it combines practical control with a bit of personality.

Build files are on GitHub, and setup instructions are available on YouTube. (more to come)

This is an independent DIY project and is not affiliated with Lumia Stream. For support, please contact AKADAZ in the Plugins section on Discord.


